PROJECT PLAN

Application Name
Online Medication & Prescription Tracker

Problem Statement:-

Many people forget to take medicines on time and find it difficult to keep their prescriptions safe. 
Paper prescriptions can be lost, and managing multiple medicines manually is confusing. 
This can lead to missed doses and health issues.

Proposed Solution :-
  
This project provides a web-based application where users can store their prescriptions digitally and manage their medicines easily. 
The system helps users track medicines and supports better medication management.

Scope of Requirements :-

The scope of this project includes:
User registration and secure login
Adding and viewing medicine details
Uploading and storing prescriptions
Viewing medication history
Secure storage of user data in a database
This project focuses on core features and is designed so that more features can be added in the future.

Technical Approach:-

The backend will be developed using Java Spring Boot to handle business logic and APIs.
The frontend will be built using React to provide a user-friendly interface.
A relational database will be used to store user, medicine, and prescription data securely.
The application will follow a step-by-step development approach starting with backend setup.

Technology Stack :-

Frontend: React
Backend: Java Spring Boot
Database: MySQL / PostgreSQL
Tools: Git, GitHub, IntelliJ IDEA, VS Code

Conclusion:-

The Online Medication & Prescription Tracker solves a real-life problem by helping users manage medicines and prescriptions digitally.
  This project also provides practical experience in full-stack web development.
